    },
    "description": "<p>After another creature you can see loses Hit Points, if they are in <strong>Crisis</strong> and are not <strong>undead</strong>, you gain <strong>1 Grave Point</strong>. You may never have more than <strong>【SL + 1】 </strong>Grave Points.</p><p>When you are reduced to 0 Hit Points, you <strong>lose all Grave Points</strong>; then, if you lost at least 1 Grave Point this way and this is the <strong>first time</strong> you are reduced to 0 HP during this scene, your current Hit Points instead become equal to <strong>【SL, multiplied by the amount of Grave Points you lost this way】</strong> .</p><hr /><p><strong>You Recover:</strong> @GAIN[(@item.level.value)+(@item.rp.current) hp]{SL × Grave Points HP}<br /><strong>Reset:</strong> @PROGRESS[beyond-the-realms-of-death reset]{Lose All Grave Points}</p>",
